* The Actual Meaning of the Fouth day is
God said let the lights be specifically placed in the firmanent of the heaven ( set in a fixed loction ), to divide the day from the night; and let them be for signs, and for seasons, anf for days and years.

* It's for the first time, he created something and didn't name it i.e Sun and star, rather than giving them names he called them greater light and lesser light 
It indicates that sun and stars are not to be worshipped in any way, in fact nothing in nature is to be worshipped . god was simply emphasising that they are not deities, they are inanimate object created by one true god. 



